snippet.title: Markom3D
snippet.description:
This channel is all about Blender and Unreal Engine 4. I am releasing three videos a week 

There will also be Live streams that I will be participating, so make sure you subscribe to the channel so that you get the notification. 

If you want to support me you can visit my Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/Markom3D
If you would like to just send me a donation for support - https://paypal.me/markom3d

If you want to check out and download some of my models - https://gumroad.com/markom3d

Facebook - https://www.facebook.com/markom3d
Instagram - https://www.instagram.com/markom3d/
Twitter - https://twitter.com/markomruki
